---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getDocBySlug } from '../../../data/navigation';

const doc = getDocBySlug('microsoft-foundry');

if (!doc) {
	throw new Error('Microsoft Foundry doc metadata is missing');
}
---

<Layout title={`${doc.title} | 通俗版 Claude Code 文档`} description={doc.summary} pathname={doc.path}>
	<article class="space-y-8">
		<header class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em]" style="color: var(--muted);">Deployment</p>
			<h1 class="mt-3 font-display text-4xl font-semibold">Microsoft Foundry</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8">{doc.summary}</p>
			<p class="mt-4 max-w-4xl leading-8" style="color: var(--muted);">
				原页来源：
				<a href="https://code.claude.com/docs/en/microsoft-foundry" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-4">官方 Microsoft Foundry</a>
			</p>
		</header>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">一句人话</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>Microsoft Foundry 就是 Azure 版的 Claude Code。用 Azure 账号登录，走 Azure 计费，跑在微软云上。</p>
				<p>适合已经在用 Azure 生态的团队，特别是用 Microsoft 365、Entra ID（原 Azure AD）的企业。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">啥时候选 Foundry</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p><strong>1. 已经在用 Azure</strong> — 账号、计费、权限都在 Azure 里。</p>
				<p><strong>2. 用 Microsoft 365</strong> — 可以用 Entra ID 统一认证。</p>
				<p><strong>3. 企业合规</strong> — Azure 的合规认证多，适合金融、政府等受监管行业。</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">怎么配置</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>设置环境变量启用 Foundry：</p>
				<div class="mt-4 rounded-[24px] border p-6 font-mono text-sm overflow-x-auto" style="border-color: var(--line); background: var(--panel-strong);">
<pre># 启用 Microsoft Foundry
export CLAUDE_CODE_USE_FOUNDRY=1
export ANTHROPIC_FOUNDRY_RESOURCE=your-resource
export ANTHROPIC_FOUNDRY_API_KEY=your-api-key

# 或者用 Entra ID 认证（不需要 API key）
# az login</pre>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="card rounded-[32px] p-8 shadow-card">
			<h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold">最后一句土话</h2>
			<div class="mt-4 space-y-4 leading-8">
				<p>Foundry 就是 Azure 生态里的 Claude Code。已经在用 Azure 就选它，不在 Azure 生态就直接用 Claude.com。</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</article>
</Layout>
